body_html: @hhwxxx I was also unable to use model.fit() with a nested Dataset iterator for multi-input and multi-output models (while using tf.keras) on version 1.10. Installing tf-gpu-nightly (my specific version is now 1.12.0-dev20180918) seemed to resolve this problem for me.

body: @hhwxxx I was also unable to use `model.fit()` with a nested Dataset iterator for multi-input and multi-output models (while using `tf.keras`) on version 1.10. Installing `tf-gpu-nightly`  (my specific version is now `1.12.0-dev20180918`) seemed to resolve this problem for me.
